_header: This time man hath overcome the fiend and robbed hell
Subjects: Christ, triumph of; Christ, Incarnation of
_description: How man is made God’s Brother — six long lines

BLHar7322.Transcription:
Þis time man haþ ouercomeÞe fend and Robbed
                    helleLoke þat on his seruiseLenger þat þou ne
                    dwelleÞis time man is made kniȝthAnd shuppare ouer alle
                    þingeLoke on non erlich þingeÞou sette þyn
                    endingeffor now is erlich man bicomeGodds owene broþerLoke
                    man on none wyseÞou chaunge for non oþer
